data.description: PRIVATE RANCH RETREAT with CASITA and expansive MOUNTAIN VIEWS AT 5200' elevation including multiple buildings for storage or hobbies,  underground electric, Rock Creek access & pond with Rock Creek water rights, mature trees, THREE SHARES IN THE RECORDED WELL AND WATER SYSTEM. NEW ROOF and NEW EXTERIOR PAINT. Home features a SimpliSafe security system, motorized security shutters, zoned Cochise RU-4 and fenced. On property is the well house w/ 10,000 gallon water storage tank. The property is DIVIDABLE and offers multiple build sites. Two entrances to property. Enjoy the wildlife, stargazing, bird watching, local history & sites, and wineries. Only 15 min to Chiricahua National Monument entrance & 30 min to Willcox. Less than one hour to the Bisbee-Douglas International Airport.
